description.descriptionShort: A 21-storey office building with a 6-storey retail/ entertainment complex.
description.descriptionLong:
Shaw House is located prominently at the intersection of Orchard Road with Scotts Road and Paterson Road. This strategic intersection is sited at the heart of the Orchard Road corridor and is linked by underpasses directly to Orchard MRT Station and Wheelock Place. Public transport is readily available along the main thoroughfares of Orchard Road with Scotts Road and Paterson Road.

Isetan, an exquisite Japanese departmental store is the anchor tenant for the retail complex whilst Shaw's flagship cinema, Lido Cineplex promotes the best ambience for audiences to catch the latest blockbusters. Mouth-watering variety of fast-food outlets and delicious treats can also be found within the complex whilst a multi-national profile of tenants occupy the office building.

description.descriptionLong:
Shaw Corner is prominently located off the junction of Boon Teck Road with Balestier Road. Being centrally located within a densley populated residential locality, it is easily accessible to the major expressways linking to the city centre and airport.

The development is currently occupied by a student hostel and has shops on its ground floor. A basement level provides car park spaces for the entire development. Being located in one of Singapore's well-known food districts, a wide variety of local delectables can be readliy found in its immediate vicinity.

For leasing enquiries, please contact Real Estate Department at +65 6235 2077 (main line).

Oriental Plaza is 4-storey commercial building strategically located at the junction of New Bridge Road with Kreta Ayer Road, within the heart of Chinatown. The development itself forms an ideal catchment area for shoppers as it is situated amongst a densely populated locality.

The development comprises primarily shops and offices with basement car parks. Outram MRT station is only a stone's throw away from the development and public transport is readily available along the main thoroughfare of New Bridge Road.

The development is centrally located in the heart of Balestier Road with easy access to the major expressways linking to the city centre, airport and ports.

Unit sizes range from 2,300 sq.ft. to 7,600 sq.ft. and have a clear ceiling height of approximately 4m with a floor loading of 14.5 KN per sq.m. However, ground floor units have a generous ceiling height of approximately 4.8 m with a floor loading of 19.0 KN per sq.m.

All floors are served by 3 X 3,000 kg cargo lifts and 1 high speed passenger lift with a capacity for 15 persons.

The development has toilet facilities on every floor and is fully equipped with Fire Protection System. All floors are treated with high quality hardeners.

Car parks can be found around the development and its loading bays (3 parking lots for 40 footer containers) are equipped with 3 X 12,270 kg capacity docklevelers.
